def meal(day,time):
if day=="sunday":
if time=="breakfast":
return "dosa"
elif time=="lunch":
return "dal rice"
elif time=="dinner":
return "paneer and chapati"
else :
return "time not found"
elif day=="monday":
if time=="breakfast":
return "fried rice"
elif time=="lunch":
return "aloo rice"
elif time=="dinner":
return "chhole bhature"
else :
return "time not found"
elif day=="other":
if time=="breakfast":
return "aloo"
elif time=="lunch":
return "rajma rice"
elif time=="dinner" :
return "veg-chapati"
else :
return "time not found"

print(meal("sunday","lunch"))
print(meal("monday","dinner"))
